Uses of Package
de.team33.libs.reflect.v4

  • Classes in de.team33.libs.reflect.v4 used by de.team33.libs.reflect.v4 
    Class and Description
    FieldMapper
    A tool that can copy instances of a certain type field by field or translate them into or from a map.
    FieldMapper.Factory
    Abstracts a factory for FieldMapper instances.
    Fields.Filter
    Provides some predefined filters for Fields.
    Fields.Mapping
    In essence, a Fields.Mapping is a Function to get a Map whose values represent a subset of all Fields declared by a given Class or one of its superclasses.
    Fields.Naming
    Defines some typical Functions that serve to find a name for a Field.
    Fields.Streaming
    Defines some typical Functions that serve to stream Fields of a given Class.
